snippet.title: Almost My Floor: Duality - Official Trailer | Ghouls 4 Games
snippet.description: Here's your look at Almost My Floor: Duality, an upcoming noir detective horror-adventure game about the internal struggle with depression and the impending darkness in a provincial town. The gameplay is based on decision-making mechanics and a branching storyline. Almost My Floor: Duality will be available on PC.
